= Story Guide =

'''Dragon Warrior''' is the first game in the series, following a lone hero on a quest to defeat the Dragonlord.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

The kingdom of Alefgard is terrorized by the Dragonlord, who has stolen the Ball of Light and kidnapped Princess Gwaelin. As a descendant of the legendary hero Erdrick, you must restore peace to the land.

