=== Rescuing Princess Gwaelin ===

# Travel to the Swamp Cave (south of castle)
# Navigate to the Dragon
# Defeat the Dragon
# Rescue Princess Gwaelin
# Return her to Tantegel Castle
# Receive Gwaelin's Love (tracks distance to castle)

=== Collecting Erdrick's Equipment ===

