=== Obtaining the Rainbow Drop ===

Requirements:
# Erdrick's Token
# Stones of Sunlight (Tantegel Castle treasure room)
# Bring both to the old man south of Rimuldar

The Rainbow Drop creates a bridge to Charlock Castle.

