== Endings ==

=== Good Ending ===

# Defeat the Dragonlord
# Recover the Ball of Light
# Return to Tantegel Castle
# Choice: become king or travel to new lands

=== Bad Ending ===

Accepting the Dragonlord's bargain results in darkness.

